      "author": "Leonezz",
      "description": "## What's New\n\n### MCP Server for AI Agent Integration\nAn embedded MCP (Model Context Protocol) server that exposes task management capabilities over Streamable HTTP transport. AI agents like Claude Code and Cursor can connect to read, create, update, and delete vault tasks.\n\n- Localhost-only binding with configurable port (default: 27182)\n- Per-request stateless transport (no resource leaks)\n- Full task CRUD via component library's capabilities module\n- Enable via `data.json`: set `mcpServer.enabled: true`\n\n### SecretStorage for API Keys\nAPI keys are now stored in Obsidian's SecretStorage instead of plaintext `data.json`. Existing keys are automatically migrated on first load.\n\n### Settings Migration Framework\nVersioned settings with automatic migration ensures forward compatibility as the settings model evolves.\n\n### Component Library Upgrade\nUpdated `@tasks-timeline/components` with new capabilities module (tools, resources, prompts) and AI system prompt support.\n\n## What's Changed\n* feat: update settings data model to v0.1.2 and integrate SecretStorage by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/25\n* feat: add MCP server and AI system prompt support by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/27\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/compare/v0.0.9...v0.1.0\n\n## What's Changed\n* feat: update settings data model to v0.1.2 and integrate SecretStorage by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/25\n* feat: add MCP server and AI system prompt support by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/27\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/compare/v0.0.9...v0.1.0\n\n## What's Changed\n* feat: update settings data model to v0.1.2 and integrate SecretStorage by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/25\n* feat: add MCP server and AI system prompt support by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/27\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/compare/v0.0.9...v0.1.0\n\n## What's Changed\n* feat: update settings data model to v0.1.2 and integrate SecretStorage by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/25\n* feat: add MCP server and AI system prompt support by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/27\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/compare/v0.0.9...v0.1.0\n\n## What's Changed\n* feat: update settings data model to v0.1.2 and integrate SecretStorage by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/25\n* feat: add MCP server and AI system prompt support by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/27\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/compare/v0.0.9...v0.1.0\n\n## What's Changed\n* feat: update settings data model to v0.1.2 and integrate SecretStorage by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/25\n* feat: add MCP server and AI system prompt support by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/27\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/compare/v0.0.9...v0.1.0\n\n## What's Changed\n* feat: update settings data model to v0.1.2 and integrate SecretStorage by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/25\n* feat: add MCP server and AI system prompt support by @Leonezz in https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/pull/27\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Leonezz/tasks-timeline-obsidian/compare/v0.0.9...v0.1.0",
